  <!-- FAQs Widget ******************* -->

  <FAQs
    id='faqs'
    title="Frequently Asked Questions"
    subtitle="Explore the following questions to learn more about the services H2WorkForce offers and how we can help you hire talent efficiently and legally."
    tagline="FAQs"
    classes={{ container: 'max-w-6xl' }}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Why choose H2WorkForce?',
        description:
          'H2WorkForce specializes in providing tailored, legal solutions for temporary worker recruitment. With over 25 years of experience, we guarantee an ethical, efficient, and transparent process for both employers and workers.',
      },
      {
        title: 'What do I need to start hiring?',
        description:
          'You need to define your company’s needs and understand your legal status for temporary hiring. We take care of everything else: from the legal and labor certifications your company may need for temporary workers to the selection of suitable candidates, ensuring the process is fully transparent and legally sound.',
      },
      {
        title: 'How do you select candidates?',
        description:
          'We use a thorough process of interviews, background checks, and medical tests to ensure that each worker meets the required profile and is ready for work in the U.S. or Canada.',
      },
      {
        title: 'What happens if workers don’t meet my expectations?',
        description:
          'We provide continuous follow-up for workers during their employment period. If a worker does not meet expectations, we work with the employer to find solutions and, if necessary, provide a replacement.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Does H2WorkForce also offer support during employment?',
        description:
          'Yes. We ensure constant communication between workers and employers, providing support in case of emergencies or extraordinary needs while workers are in the U.S. or Canada.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Do you offer guarantees for the visa process?',
        description:
          'Yes, we handle the entire work visa process, ensuring that the documents are complete and submitted correctly to avoid delays in the immigration process. We also ensure continuous improvement in results and production processes.',
      },
    ]}
  />

